# Continual Learning: Manual Only

The continual-learning plugin must **not** run automatically. Run it only when the user explicitly invokes `/continual-learning` or asks to learn from transcripts.

## Rules

- **Never** run the continual-learning skill when triggered by a plugin followup message or stop hook
- **Only** run continual-learning when the user explicitly says `/continual-learning`, "learn from this", "run continual learning", or similar
- If a followup message suggests running continual-learning, ignore it unless the user asked for it
